title: Bloomberg Markets 12/23/2025
description: "Bloomberg Markets" follows the market moves across every global asset class and discusses the biggest issues for Wall Street. Today's guests: StoneX Financial Chief Markets Strategist Kathryn Rooney Vera, Bloomberg's Stuart Paul and Maxwell Adler.  (Source: Bloomberg)
